reviewText: There is a NOT so secret film community located in California, that produces certain films that can and should be seen by Adults ONLY.  Into this community some of the most beautiful and talented actresses in the world flock to become seen by both men and women alike.  There are also a great deal of men who work in this industry.  The actor's who appear in these films are all ages, and the women who star in these films can give any Hollywood starlet a run for their money.  The film scripts are well written, dramas, comedies, science fiction, love stories, the costumes are well done, and the subject of the films isn't always surrounded by the three little word SEX.  One of those actresses is a woman by the name of Jennifer Welles.  A brunette beauty with deep eyes and a quick smile.
